name: Numinus Wellness Inc.
longDescription: Numinus Wellness Inc develops proprietary, psychedelic-centered, therapeutic products and services through its own laboratory and research & development processes. The company's clinic network consists of Numinus Health, Mindspace Services and the Neurology Center of Toronto. Its services include Ketamine-assisted psychotherapy for depression, neurological care and psychotherapy and counselling by registered psychologists.
